hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections

Class ArrayBackedIndexedCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.ArrayBackedIndexedCollection

  • public class ArrayBackedIndexedCollection
extends Object
    This class implementation of resizable array-backed collection of objects. Duplicate elements are allowed and null references are not allowed.
    Author:
    Vilim Staroveški
